  section#banner
    .inner.align-center
      .logo
        img(src='images/logo.png')
      h2(hidden='') Ballinlough Dental Care
      p.
        Taking care of the dental health of the people of Ballinlough, Ballintemple
        and the surrounding area of Cork City for over thirty years.
        
        a.button(href='#') http://www.ballinloughdentalcare.ie/contact
